(ns farsund.theme.events
  (:require [re-frame.core :as rf]
            [cuerdas.core :as str]
            [farsund.theme.db :as theme.db]
            [farsund.utils.core :as u]))


(rf/reg-event-db
  :theme/init-db
  (fn [db _]
    (merge db theme.db/state)))


(rf/reg-event-db
  :theme/set
  (fn [db [_ theme]]
    (assoc db :theme (-> theme
                         (js->clj :keywordize-keys true)
                         (u/transform-keys str/keyword)))))
